    <h3 style="color: white; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Hidden Feature: Plain Text QR Codes</h3>
    <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
